Glossary:

 =Package=     -  File archive, the  'qdev' toolkit and/or related material.
 =Project=     -  Quick Development Suite  also known as  'qdev'  for short.
 =Components=  -  All package  files except for  the ones  licensed already.
 =Binaries=    -  All files that contain 'qdev' library or header code/data.
 =Group=       -  Burnt Chip Dominators aka  BCD  current cult members only.
